From Beer Garden get-togethers to fun workshops ‚Äì we love to bring people together at Playalinda Brewing Company.
Our Playalinda Brewing Company Taproom regularly features an evolving lineup of fun things to do. Our proximity to the Canaveral National Seashore, Kennedy Space Center, Indian River Lagoon and tropical beaches provide ample opportunity for active, outdoor adventures ‚Äì something we take full advantage of whenever possible.
The best way to stay on top of upcoming Playalinda events is to follow the Playalinda Brewing Company on
Facebook
and
Instagram
. You can also scope out what‚Äôs coming up right here!
Regular Playalinda events range from Tuesday Night Trivia, special beer releases, local vendor markets, live music, and craft workshops.
Our Playalinda Brewing Company taproom is located a short drive from local hot spots like Melbourne, Orlando, Cocoa Beach and Daytona Beach ‚Äì making it easy to access the brewery from anywhere in Central Florida.
